annotation.text:
Each prm org only has only one post.
App maintenance: Same user accounts must be in both - Homes Opportunity Referral Program Compliance Granters group - Forums Opportunity Referral Program Enrollment Granters group

`prmorganization` status values:
The business rules work on these meanings: Active : Legal has declared valid Inactive: In forms where someone can set some criteria active and not others, this criterion has not been validated Rejected: Previously rejected. Homes Opportunity Referral Program Compliance Granters group has declared invalid via the review enrollment request task. In Progress: Partner has submitted enrollment request, and Legal has not yet evaluated. <null> No workflow ever done on this criterion.
Currently, If practitioner is missing prmorg, there is no catch flow.

ABA-3177 For the deployment of the enrollment process, the first deployment will only be accessible to ABA
ABA makes enrollment request then bypass tempo post creation and DB save.
In release where Inactive value used, also overwrite Inactive with In Progress
